Package axyz.gameofgoose.game

Class Summary
Action Abstract class that represent an Action in a Game.
Game Abstract class that represent a generic Game.
GameState Abstract class that represent a generic state of a game.
GOGAction Class that represent the actions in a game of the goose.
GOGBridgeRule Implementation of the rule of the bridge: if you go in the box 6 you cross directly to the 12.
GOGDeathRule Implementation of the rule of the death: if you go in the box 58 you die and return to the 1.
GOGDefaultRule Implementation of the default rule where you advance by the number that you obtain throwing the dices.
GOGGame Class that represent a game of the goose.
GOGGameState Class that represent the state a game of the goose.
GOGGooseRule Implementation of the goose rule where you advance by the double of the number that you obtain throwing the dices.
GOGLabyrinthRule Implementation of the labyrinth rule where you go in the box 42 you get lost and arrive at the box 39.
GOGPlayer Class that represent the player in a game of the goose.
GOGRule Alass that represent a rule in the game of the goose.
GOGRuleBook Class that represent the rule book of the game of the goose.
Player Abstract class that represent a generic player.
Rule Abstract class that represent a generic Rule.
RuleBook Abstract class that represent a generic RuleBook.
